{
  "video_id": "Hh09xlzxRmE",
  "title": "My year reading a book from every country in the world | Ann Morgan",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13000.0,
      "end_time": 15903.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s often said that you can tell a lot about a person"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15927.0,
      "end_time": 18422.0,
      "text": "by looking at what&#39;s on their bookshelves."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19679.0,
      "end_time": 21665.0,
      "text": "What do my bookshelves say about me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22402.0,
      "end_time": 26860.0,
      "text": "Well, when I asked myself this question a few years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26110.0,
      "end_time": 28411.0,
      "text": "I made an alarming discovery."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29131.0,
      "end_time": 32134.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d always thought of myself as a fairly cultured,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32159.0,
      "end_time": 34583.0,
      "text": "cosmopolitan sort of person."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34608.0,
      "end_time": 37703.0,
      "text": "But my bookshelves told a rather different story."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38439.0,
      "end_time": 40910.0,
      "text": "Pretty much all the titles on them"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40115.0,
      "end_time": 42974.0,
      "text": "were by British or North American authors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42998.0,
      "end_time": 45534.0,
      "text": "and there was almost nothing in translation."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46327.0,
      "end_time": 50177.0,
      "text": "Discovering this massive, cultural blind spot in my reading"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 50201.0,
      "end_time": 52200.0,
      "text": "came as quite a shock."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52260.0,
      "end_time": 55519.0,
      "text": "And when I thought about it, it seemed like a real shame."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 55543.0,
      "end_time": 58915.0,
      "text": "I knew there had to be lots of amazing stories out there"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 58939.0,
      "end_time": 62316.0,
      "text": "by writers working in languages other than English."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 62340.0,
      "end_time": 65642.0,
      "text": "And it seemed really sad to think that my reading habits meant"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 65666.0,
      "end_time": 68230.0,
      "text": "I would probably never encounter them."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 68435.0,
      "end_time": 71301.0,
      "text": "So, I decided to prescribe myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 71325.0,
      "end_time": 73943.0,
      "text": "an intensive course of global reading."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 74602.0,
      "end_time": 78340.0,
      "text": "2012 was set to be a very international year for the UK;"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 78364.0,
      "end_time": 80436.0,
      "text": "it was the year of the London Olympics."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 80460.0,
      "end_time": 83982.0,
      "text": "And so I decided to use it as my time frame"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 84600.0,
      "end_time": 87213.0,
      "text": "to try to read a novel, short story collection"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 87237.0,
      "end_time": 91554.0,
      "text": "or memoir from every country in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 92771.0,
      "end_time": 94104.0,
      "text": "And so I did."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 94128.0,
      "end_time": 95755.0,
      "text": "And it was very exciting"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 95779.0,
      "end_time": 97675.0,
      "text": "and I learned some remarkable things"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 97699.0,
      "end_time": 99814.0,
      "text": "and made some wonderful connections"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 99838.0,
      "end_time": 101707.0,
      "text": "that I want to share with you today."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 102880.0,
      "end_time": 105285.0,
      "text": "But it started with some practical problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 105849.0,
      "end_time": 110516.0,
      "text": "After I&#39;d worked out which of the many different lists of countries in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 110540.0,
      "end_time": 112746.0,
      "text": "to use for my project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 112770.0,
      "end_time": 115920.0,
      "text": "I ended up going with the list of UN-recognized nations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 115944.0,
      "end_time": 117167.0,
      "text": "to which I added Taiwan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 117191.0,
      "end_time": 120547.0,
      "text": "which gave me a total of 196 countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 121143.0,
      "end_time": 123998.0,
      "text": "And after I&#39;d worked out how to fit reading and blogging"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 124220.0,
      "end_time": 126332.0,
      "text": "about, roughly, four books a week"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 126356.0,
      "end_time": 129466.0,
      "text": "around working five days a week,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 129491.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133195.0,
      "text": "I then had to face up to the fact that I might even not be able"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 133219.0,
      "end_time": 135947.0,
      "text": "to get books in English from every country."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 136546.0,
      "end_time": 140291.0,
      "text": "Only around 4.5 percent of the literary works published"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 140315.0,
      "end_time": 142966.0,
      "text": "each year in the UK are translations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 142990.0,
      "end_time": 146616.0,
      "text": "and the figures are similar for much of the English-speaking world."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 146640.0,
      "end_time": 149593.0,
      "text": "Although, the proportion of translated books published"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 149617.0,
      "end_time": 152409.0,
      "text": "in many other countries is a lot higher."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 153101.0,
      "end_time": 156409.0,
      "text": "4.5 percent is tiny enough to start with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 156433.0,
      "end_time": 158268.0,
      "text": "but what that figure doesn&#39;t tell you"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 158292.0,
      "end_time": 160965.0,
      "text": "is that many of those books will come from countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 160989.0,
      "end_time": 163163.0,
      "text": "with strong publishing networks"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 163187.0,
      "end_time": 167354.0,
      "text": "and lots of industry professionals primed to go out and sell those titles"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 167378.0,
      "end_time": 169338.0,
      "text": "to English-language publishers."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 169711.0,
      "end_time": 174283.0,
      "text": "So, for example, although well over 100 books are translated from French"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 174307.0,
      "end_time": 176209.0,
      "text": "and published in the UK each year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 176234.0,
      "end_time": 180647.0,
      "text": "most of them will come from countries like France or Switzerland."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 181107.0,
      "end_time": 183845.0,
      "text": "French-speaking Africa, on the other hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 183869.0,
      "end_time": 185511.0,
      "text": "will rarely ever get a look-in."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 186284.0,
      "end_time": 189607.0,
      "text": "The upshot is that there are actually quite a lot of nations"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 189631.0,
      "end_time": 193262.0,
      "text": "that may have little or even no commercially available literature"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 193286.0,
      "end_time": 194439.0,
      "text": "in English."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 195740.0,
      "end_time": 198140.0,
      "text": "Their books remain invisible to readers"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 198164.0,
      "end_time": 201100.0,
      "text": "of the world&#39;s most published language."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 202200.0,
      "end_time": 203820.0,
      "text": "But when it came to reading the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 203844.0,
      "end_time": 205614.0,
      "text": "the biggest challenge of all for me"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 205638.0,
      "end_time": 208772.0,
      "text": "was that fact that I didn&#39;t know where to start."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 209201.0,
      "end_time": 212559.0,
      "text": "Having spent my life reading almost exclusively British"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 212583.0,
      "end_time": 214232.0,
      "text": "and North American books,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 214256.0,
      "end_time": 217845.0,
      "text": "I had no idea how to go about sourcing and finding stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 217869.0,
      "end_time": 220580.0,
      "text": "and choosing them from much of the rest of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 220604.0,
      "end_time": 223989.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t tell you how to source a story from Swaziland."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 224130.0,
      "end_time": 226648.0,
      "text": "I wouldn&#39;t know a good novel from Namibia."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 227125.0,
      "end_time": 228718.0,
      "text": "There was no hiding it --"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 228742.0,
      "end_time": 232650.0,
      "text": "I was a clueless literary xenophobe."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 232541.0,
      "end_time": 234995.0,
      "text": "So how on earth was I going to read the world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 235777.0,
      "end_time": 237634.0,
      "text": "I was going to have to ask for help."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 237658.0,
      "end_time": 241156.0,
      "text": "So in October 2011, I registered my blog,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 241181.0,
      "end_time": 242952.0,
      "text": "ayearofreadingtheworld.com,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 242976.0,
      "end_time": 245461.0,
      "text": "and I posted a short appeal online."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 245863.0,
      "end_time": 247920.0,
      "text": "I explained who I was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 247116.0,
      "end_time": 249124.0,
      "text": "how narrow my reading had been,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 249148.0,
      "end_time": 251500.0,
      "text": "and I asked anyone who cared to"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 251290.0,
      "end_time": 253594.0,
      "text": "to leave a message suggesting what I might read"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 253618.0,
      "end_time": 255302.0,
      "text": "from other parts of the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 255913.0,
      "end_time": 259986.0,
      "text": "Now, I had no idea whether anyone would be interested,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 260100.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263123.0,
      "text": "but within a few hours of me posting that appeal online,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 263148.0,
      "end_time": 265584.0,
      "text": "people started to get in touch."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 265608.0,
      "end_time": 268106.0,
      "text": "At first, it was friends and colleagues."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 268466.0,
      "end_time": 270170.0,
      "text": "Then it was friends of friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 270383.0,
      "end_time": 272659.0,
      "text": "And pretty soon, it was strangers."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 273399.0,
      "end_time": 276201.0,
      "text": "Four days after I put that appeal online,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 276225.0,
      "end_time": 279956.0,
      "text": "I got a message from a woman called Rafidah in Kuala Lumpur."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 280292.0,
      "end_time": 282967.0,
      "text": "She said she loved the sound of my project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 282991.0,
      "end_time": 285890.0,
      "text": "could she go to her local English-language bookshop"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 285914.0,
      "end_time": 289204.0,
      "text": "and choose my Malaysian book and post it to me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 289912.0,
      "end_time": 291664.0,
      "text": "I accepted enthusiastically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 291689.0,
      "end_time": 293191.0,
      "text": "and a few weeks later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 293215.0,
      "end_time": 297763.0,
      "text": "a package arrived containing not one, but two books --"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 299263.0,
      "end_time": 301681.0,
      "text": "Rafidah&#39;s choice from Malaysia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 302908.0,
      "end_time": 306791.0,
      "text": "and a book from Singapore that she had also picked out for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 308428.0,
      "end_time": 310865.0,
      "text": "Now, at the time, I was amazed"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 310889.0,
      "end_time": 314465.0,
      "text": "that a stranger more than 6,000 miles away"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 314489.0,
      "end_time": 316414.0,
      "text": "would go to such lengths to help someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 316438.0,
      "end_time": 318497.0,
      "text": "she would probably never meet."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 319100.0,
      "end_time": 322751.0,
      "text": "But Rafidah&#39;s kindness proved to be the pattern for that year."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 323240.0,
      "end_time": 326530.0,
      "text": "Time and again, people went out of their way to help me."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 327226.0,
      "end_time": 329835.0,
      "text": "Some took on research on my behalf,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 329859.0,
      "end_time": 332882.0,
      "text": "and others made detours on holidays and business trips"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 332906.0,
      "end_time": 334842.0,
      "text": "to go to bookshops for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 335526.0,
      "end_time": 338762.0,
      "text": "It turns out, if you want to read the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 338786.0,
      "end_time": 342187.0,
      "text": "if you want to encounter it with an open mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 342211.0,
      "end_time": 344141.0,
      "text": "the world will help you."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 345118.0,
      "end_time": 346332.0,
      "text": "When it came to countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 346357.0,
      "end_time": 349863.0,
      "text": "with little or no commercially available literature in English,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 349887.0,
      "end_time": 351700.0,
      "text": "people went further still."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 352689.0,
      "end_time": 355901.0,
      "text": "Books often came from surprising sources."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 356536.0,
      "end_time": 359575.0,
      "text": "My Panamanian read, for example, came through a conversation"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 359599.0,
      "end_time": 362618.0,
      "text": "I had with the Panama Canal on Twitter."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 363497.0,
      "end_time": 367700.0,
      "text": "Yes, the Panama Canal has a Twitter account."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 367731.0,
      "end_time": 370105.0,
      "text": "And when I tweeted at it about my project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 370129.0,
      "end_time": 373508.0,
      "text": "it suggested that I might like to try and get hold of the work"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 373532.0,
      "end_time": 376111.0,
      "text": "of the Panamanian author Juan David Morgan."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 376898.0,
      "end_time": 379468.0,
      "text": "I found Morgan&#39;s website and I sent him a message,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 379492.0,
      "end_time": 381924.0,
      "text": "asking if any of his Spanish-language novels"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 381948.0,
      "end_time": 383938.0,
      "text": "had been translated into English."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 384432.0,
      "end_time": 386863.0,
      "text": "And he said that nothing had been published,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 386887.0,
      "end_time": 389317.0,
      "text": "but he did have an unpublished translation"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 389341.0,
      "end_time": 391325.0,
      "text": "of his novel \"The Golden Horse.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 391887.0,
      "end_time": 393225.0,
      "text": "He emailed this to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 393249.0,
      "end_time": 396383.0,
      "text": "allowing me to become one of the first people ever"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 396407.0,
      "end_time": 398251.0,
      "text": "to read that book in English."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 398929.0,
      "end_time": 401578.0,
      "text": "Morgan was by no means the only wordsmith"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 401603.0,
      "end_time": 403593.0,
      "text": "to share his work with me in this way."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 404150.0,
      "end_time": 405777.0,
      "text": "From Sweden to Palau,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 405801.0,
      "end_time": 409792.0,
      "text": "writers and translators sent me self-published books"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 409816.0,
      "end_time": 411546.0,
      "text": "and unpublished manuscripts of books"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 411570.0,
      "end_time": 414450.0,
      "text": "that hadn&#39;t been picked up by Anglophone publishers"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 414474.0,
      "end_time": 416496.0,
      "text": "or that were no longer available,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 416520.0,
      "end_time": 421228.0,
      "text": "giving me privileged glimpses of some remarkable imaginary worlds."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 422800.0,
      "end_time": 423159.0,
      "text": "I read, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 423183.0,
      "end_time": 427772.0,
      "text": "about the Southern African king Ngungunhane, who led the resistance"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 427797.0,
      "end_time": 430459.0,
      "text": "against the Portuguese in the 19th century;"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 431113.0,
      "end_time": 433884.0,
      "text": "and about marriage rituals in a remote village"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 433908.0,
      "end_time": 436906.0,
      "text": "on the shores of the Caspian sea in Turkmenistan."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 438524.0,
      "end_time": 442133.0,
      "text": "I met Kuwait&#39;s answer to Bridget Jones."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 442450.0,
      "end_time": 444450.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 445301.0,
      "end_time": 448866.0,
      "text": "And I read about an orgy in a tree in Angola."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 452870.0,
      "end_time": 455220.0,
      "text": "But perhaps the most amazing example"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 455460.0,
      "end_time": 457450.0,
      "text": "of the lengths that people were prepared to go to"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 457474.0,
      "end_time": 459101.0,
      "text": "to help me read the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 459125.0,
      "end_time": 461574.0,
      "text": "came towards the end of my quest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 461598.0,
      "end_time": 465432.0,
      "text": "when I tried to get hold of a book from the tiny, Portuguese-speaking"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 465456.0,
      "end_time": 468723.0,
      "text": "African island nation of São Tomé and Príncipe."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 469364.0,
      "end_time": 473130.0,
      "text": "Now, having spent several months trying everything I could think of to find"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 473370.0,
      "end_time": 476376.0,
      "text": "a book that had been translated into English from the nation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 476400.0,
      "end_time": 478642.0,
      "text": "it seemed as though the only option left to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 478666.0,
      "end_time": 481873.0,
      "text": "was to see if I could get something translated for me from scratch."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 482404.0,
      "end_time": 483905.0,
      "text": "Now, I was really dubious"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 483929.0,
      "end_time": 486325.0,
      "text": "whether anyone was going to want to help with this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 486349.0,
      "end_time": 488848.0,
      "text": "and give up their time for something like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 489525.0,
      "end_time": 493787.0,
      "text": "But, within a week of me putting a call out on Twitter and Facebook"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 493812.0,
      "end_time": 495766.0,
      "text": "for Portuguese speakers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 495790.0,
      "end_time": 499361.0,
      "text": "I had more people than I could involve in the project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 499385.0,
      "end_time": 503743.0,
      "text": "including Margaret Jull Costa, a leader in her field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 503767.0,
      "end_time": 509680.0,
      "text": "who has translated the work of Nobel Prize winner José Saramago."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 510443.0,
      "end_time": 512377.0,
      "text": "With my nine volunteers in place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 512402.00000000006,
      "end_time": 514990.00000000006,
      "text": "I managed to find a book by a São Toméan author"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 515140.0,
      "end_time": 517524.0,
      "text": "that I could buy enough copies of online."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 517548.0,
      "end_time": 518702.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s one of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 519268.0,
      "end_time": 522832.0,
      "text": "And I sent a copy out to each of my volunteers."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 522856.0,
      "end_time": 526300.0,
      "text": "They all took on a couple of short stories from this collection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 526540.0,
      "end_time": 529680.0,
      "text": "stuck to their word, sent their translations back to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 529705.0,
      "end_time": 533494.0,
      "text": "and within six weeks, I had the entire book to read."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 534422.0,
      "end_time": 538884.0,
      "text": "In that case, as I found so often during my year of reading the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 538908.0,
      "end_time": 542993.0,
      "text": "my not knowing and being open about my limitations"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 543170.0,
      "end_time": 545158.0,
      "text": "had become a big opportunity."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 545935.0,
      "end_time": 548122.0,
      "text": "When it came to São Tomé and Príncipe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 548146.0,
      "end_time": 551492.0,
      "text": "it was a chance not only to learn something new"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 551516.0,
      "end_time": 554190.0,
      "text": "and discover a new collection of stories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 554215.0,
      "end_time": 557161.0,
      "text": "but also to bring together a group of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 557185.0,
      "end_time": 560414.0,
      "text": "and facilitate a joint creative endeavor."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 560901.0,
      "end_time": 564800.0,
      "text": "My weakness had become the project&#39;s strength."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 565929.0,
      "end_time": 569485.0,
      "text": "The books I read that year opened my eyes to many things."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 569509.0,
      "end_time": 571696.0,
      "text": "As those who enjoy reading will know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 571720.0,
      "end_time": 575500.0,
      "text": "books have an extraordinary power to take you out of yourself"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 575524.0,
      "end_time": 577668.0,
      "text": "and into someone else&#39;s mindset,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 577692.0,
      "end_time": 579534.0,
      "text": "so that, for a while at least,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 579558.0,
      "end_time": 581783.0,
      "text": "you look at the world through different eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 582390.0,
      "end_time": 584853.0,
      "text": "That can be an uncomfortable experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 584877.0,
      "end_time": 586649.0,
      "text": "particularly if you&#39;re reading a book"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 586673.0,
      "end_time": 590970.0,
      "text": "from a culture that may have quite different values to your own."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 590601.0,
      "end_time": 592750.0,
      "text": "But it can also be really enlightening."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 593402.0,
      "end_time": 597316.0,
      "text": "Wrestling with unfamiliar ideas can help clarify your own thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 597742.0,
      "end_time": 599909.0,
      "text": "And it can also show up blind spots"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 599933.0,
      "end_time": 602575.0,
      "text": "in the way you might have been looking at the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 603720.0,
      "end_time": 605954.0,
      "text": "When I looked back at much of the English-language literature"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 605978.0,
      "end_time": 607664.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d grown up with, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 607688.0,
      "end_time": 610725.0,
      "text": "I began to see how narrow a lot of it was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 610749.0,
      "end_time": 613561.0,
      "text": "compared to the richness that the world has to offer."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 614886.0,
      "end_time": 617480.0,
      "text": "And as the pages turned,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 617720.0,
      "end_time": 619538.0,
      "text": "something else started to happen, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 620150.0,
      "end_time": 621300.0,
      "text": "Little by little,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 621325.0,
      "end_time": 625610.0,
      "text": "that long list of countries that I&#39;d started the year with, changed"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 625634.0,
      "end_time": 629993.0,
      "text": "from a rather dry, academic register of place names"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 630170.0,
      "end_time": 632698.0,
      "text": "into living, breathing entities."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 633475.0,
      "end_time": 636198.0,
      "text": "Now, I don&#39;t want to suggest that it&#39;s at all possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 636222.0,
      "end_time": 640428.0,
      "text": "to get a rounded picture of a country simply by reading one book."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 641100.0,
      "end_time": 644599.0,
      "text": "But cumulatively, the stories I read that year"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 644623.0,
      "end_time": 647683.0,
      "text": "made me more alive than ever before"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 647707.0,
      "end_time": 653781.0,
      "text": "to the richness, diversity and complexity of our remarkable planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 654654.0,
      "end_time": 656647.0,
      "text": "It was as though the world&#39;s stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 656671.0,
      "end_time": 660571.0,
      "text": "and the people who&#39;d gone to such lengths to help me read them"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 660595.0,
      "end_time": 662500.0,
      "text": "had made it real to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 664860.0,
      "end_time": 666621.0,
      "text": "These days, when I look at my bookshelves"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 666645.0,
      "end_time": 669770.0,
      "text": "or consider the works on my e-reader,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 669794.0,
      "end_time": 671909.0,
      "text": "they tell a rather different story."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 672649.0,
      "end_time": 675995.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the story of the power books have to connect us"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 676190.0,
      "end_time": 680764.0,
      "text": "across political, geographical, cultural, social, religious divides."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 681422.0,
      "end_time": 685564.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the tale of the potential human beings have to work together."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 686320.0,
      "end_time": 687662.0,
      "text": "And, it&#39;s testament"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 687686.0,
      "end_time": 692309.0,
      "text": "to the extraordinary times we live in, where, thanks to the Internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 692333.0,
      "end_time": 694250.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s easier than ever before"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 694274.0,
      "end_time": 698703.0,
      "text": "for a stranger to share a story, a worldview, a book"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 698727.0,
      "end_time": 702520.0,
      "text": "with someone she may never meet, on the other side of the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 703595.0,
      "end_time": 706693.0,
      "text": "I hope it&#39;s a story I&#39;m reading for many years to come."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 707740.0,
      "end_time": 709923.0,
      "text": "And I hope many more people will join me."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 709947.0,
      "end_time": 712561.0,
      "text": "If we all read more widely, there&#39;d be more incentive"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 712585.0,
      "end_time": 715132.0,
      "text": "for publishers to translate more books,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 715156.0,
      "end_time": 717940.0,
      "text": "and we would all be richer for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 717713.0,
      "end_time": 718870.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 718894.0,
      "end_time": 722628.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}